voice_assistant/
├── app.py               # Flask entry point
├── config.py            # Configuration settings
├── audio.py             # Speech input/output
├── nlp.py               # Response generation (Groq)
├── intents.py           # Intent detection logic
├── services.py          # URL mappings and matching
├── actions.py           # System/web actions
├── history.py           # Chat history management
└── templates/
    └── index.html       # Optional Flask UI
